            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:b4015a97-4548-47d1-8e27-9fec008cd3b9</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/vibration_analysis/~3/FbMsZwGAe0c/orbits-condition-monitoring</link>
