            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:248dd868-a328-4d78-a64d-9f12009f37da</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/vibration_analysis/~3/byFwSWtwHrQ/Drilling-Platforms-Vibration-Analysis</link>
