            <title>Vibration analysis and PdM with RFID tags</title>
            <description>&lt;p id="eow-description"&gt;
	This video outlines how maintenance technicians can perform vibration analysis and predictive maintenance with RFID tags.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/vibration_analysis/~4/NVxO2HrFzyU" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
            <a10:updated>2010-10-26T08:20:20-05:00</a10:updated>
