            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:6ac829ac-0795-4c33-97dc-9ddc009f3f8e</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/vibration_analysis/~3/e46vx2i-TYY/vibration-analysis-maintenance</link>
