            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:d413937a-a224-424c-942c-9db40096b07c</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/vibration_analysis/~3/PfXlOiGJmak/Datastick-machine-vibration-seminar</link>
