            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:0e1fd342-4c88-47a3-a611-9d9c008a6207</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/vibration_analysis/~3/fJhN6E0M6X4/Azima-Panama-vibration-monitoring</link>
