            <title>Vibration analysis as a key component of a PdM program</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;span&gt;Mike Anderson of Newark, Ohio-based Anderson Engineering describes the technologies of a predictive maintenance program and the benefits such a program can bring to the modern factory.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
