&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;Electric Motors Performance Analysis Testing Tool Demonstration Project, Pacific Gas &amp;amp; Electric, 2001.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;Industrial Productivity Training Manual, 1996 Annual IAC Directors Meeting, Rutgers University, U.S. Department of Energy Office of Industrial Technologies, 1996.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;sup&gt;4&lt;/sup&gt;Electric Motors Performance Analysis Testing Tool Demonstration Project, Pacific Gas &amp;amp; Electric, 2001.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;sup&gt;5&lt;/sup&gt;Electric Motors Performance Analysis Testing Tool Demonstration Project, Pacific Gas &amp;amp; Electric, 2001.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;sup&gt;6&lt;/sup&gt;MotorMaster Plus is a free motor energy and management software available through the U.S. Department of Energy; &lt;a href="http://www.oit.doe.gov/bestpractices/"&gt;www.oit.doe.gov/bestpractices/&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
