            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:9001497e-9905-4e42-9a08-9cf800da1c41</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/vibration_analysis/~3/GVQB1yAScjY/vibration-analyzer-bearing</link>
